snippet.title: Tech Support: Error Unknown - Announcement Trailer
snippet.description:
Tech Support: Error Unknown is available on Steam: http://bit.ly/2rsf0uJ
Official website: https://techsupportgame.com/

Things are not what they seem at your new tech support specialist job. While resolving customer issues, you soon find yourself in the middle of a conspiracy. Will you side with your employer, join a rogue hacktivist group bent on destroying them, assist the police or stand alone?

Facebook: https://www.facebook.com/Tech-Support-Error-Unknown-527632034344154/

Twitter: https://twitter.com/dragon_slumber / http://twitter.com/Iceberg_Int #TechSupportGame

Steam Publisher Page: http://bit.ly/IcebergOnSteam

Reddit: https://www.reddit.com/r/TechSupportGame/

Stay up to date with Iceberg Interactive! Sign up for our newsletter here: http://eepurl.com/cXFsK9
